.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>Podsumowuj\u0105c,<\/b> nowe mo\u017cliwo\u015bci, jakie daje Amazon, mog\u0105 znacz\u0105co wp\u0142yn\u0105\u0107 na Twoj\u0105 sprzeda\u017c. Wykorzystaj wirtualne zestawy, aby zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 widoczno\u015b\u0107 swoich produkt\u00f3w i przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 wi\u0119cej klient\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><b>Jak wykorzysta\u0107 nowe funkcje Amazon do zwi\u0119kszenia sprzeda\u017cy?<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Czy wiesz, \u017ce Amazon wprowadza<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7530,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7529","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-ecommerce"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7529"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7529"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7529\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7530"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7529"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7529"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7529"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}